    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建造你的家园 </h2>大胆梦想，创造一个你想要的家，把你的农场变成你想要的任何东西。 从头开始设计、<br>制作和定制你自己的家园。无论你是建造房屋、布置花园还是设计舒适的角落，你的家都<br>反映了你的个人风格和创造力。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891280/extras/25a90490d3be550926ac4e70c3a26e25.poster.avif?t=1759866883\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891280/extras/25a90490d3be550926ac4e70c3a26e25.webm?t=1759866883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891280/extras/25a90490d3be550926ac4e70c3a26e25.mp4?t=1759866883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >管理和交朋友</h2>从平凡到非凡，培育多元化的动物园。每种动物都有自己的个性，并把这种个性传递到父<br>母与孩子之间。探索你的世界，找到具有独一无二特征的野生动物来收集。你能养出完美<br>的草莓牛吗？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891280/extras/ce70d2670b2bbe23501d68c2448efe3f.poster.avif?t=1759866883\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891280/extras/ce70d2670b2bbe23501d68c2448efe3f.webm?t=1759866883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891280/extras/ce70d2670b2bbe23501d68c2448efe3f.mp4?t=1759866883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多人合作游戏 </h2>通过多人合作游戏将你的朋友带入你的世界。一起耕种、建造、装饰和探索。共享资源，<br>协作开展项目，并在真正互联的体验中共同享受社区活动。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891280/extras/9cd7a59fc29cfaa5ed2baca0b7f4309a.poster.avif?t=1759866883\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891280/extras/9cd7a59fc29cfaa5ed2baca0b7f4309a.webm?t=1759866883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891280/extras/9cd7a59fc29cfaa5ed2baca0b7f4309a.mp4?t=1759866883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >手工制作一个亲密开放的世界</h2>探索一个手工制作的亲密开放世界，每条路径都通向新的发现。从熙熙攘攘的小镇到郁郁<br>葱葱的森林、隐蔽的小树林和深邃神秘的洞穴 - 探索每个地区的秘密和故事。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891280/extras/97cbc48fd1dda34c998363bc4be7640f.poster.avif?t=1759866883\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891280/extras/97cbc48fd1dda34c998363bc4be7640f.webm?t=1759866883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891280/extras/97cbc48fd1dda34c998363bc4be7640f.mp4?t=1759866883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >成为社区的一部分 </h2>在Everbloom的世界里，美味的食物已经被时间遗忘了。作为新人，你必须追踪并重新发现丢失的传家宝，让世界重拾美味。与一群色彩斑斓的角色互动，他们将 Everbloom 的世界带入生活。建立友谊，帮助你的邻居，并邀请镇上的人一起聚会，成为社区中不可或缺的一部分，让这个社区在你的参与下发展壮大。<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891280/extras/aac5e7a48667628974da04170590185e.poster.avif?t=1759866883\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891280/extras/aac5e7a48667628974da04170590185e.webm?t=1759866883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891280/extras/aac5e7a48667628974da04170590185e.mp4?t=1759866883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features: </strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>钓鱼：探索世界并捕捉各种鱼类。<br></li><li>烹饪：混合和匹配调料，直到获得完美的结果。<br></li><li>花卉育种：混合种子颜色以种出独特的花色。 <br></li><li>制作和建造：建造家具、房屋、设备和工具等所有东西。<br></li><li>市民：与镇民交朋友，为你的冒险注入活力。每个角色都有独特的故事和秘密。 <br></li><li>浪漫：约会并建立可能持续一生的联系。   <br></li><li>定制：从各种动物类型、颜色和服装选项中进行挑选，以反映出你的个人风格。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891280/extras/25a44271fc4ac9443fc446d9132577d1.avif?t=1759866883\" width=600 height=400 /></span>",
